VETERANS ARE HELPING COGNIZANT CREATE A NEW TOMORROW.
Hiring veterans makes America—and Cognizant—stronger. We recognize that veterans are a great fit for Cognizant, and we continuously demonstrate our support and commitment to veterans as they return from service and begin the transition back into civilian life. Assisting veterans in finding employment at Cognizant is one of the key roles we play in ensuring veterans can successfully join the corporate world.
We participate in state and national partnerships—hiring events and career conferences—and we have an active network of military employees proudly named the Cognizant Veterans Network. We are dedicated to leveraging and promoting the unmatched skills and experiences that veterans bring to Cognizant. We feel privileged to be an integral part of their transition to corporate America.
Veterans make talented employees—their experience in the military equips them with the leadership, conﬁdence and teaming abilities that can be gained in very few environments.
Every day our veterans play a vital role at Cognizant. And in return, Cognizant offers veterans experiences they seek—including exposure to a variety of industries in a short period of time, the opportunity to build upon their skills in a business environment and the ability to gain valuable business insights by tackling our clients’ most critical issues.






Cognizant Joins Coalition Dedicated to Employing Veterans
Cognizant Technology Solutions is a coalition member of the Veteran Jobs Mission. This coalition participates in a collective initiative to hire 200,000 transitioning service members and military veterans by the year 2020. As a coalition member, Cognizant is proud to commit to the effort of providing career opportunities for United States veterans.
For more information on the initiative and for veteran career resources, visit Veteran Jobs Mission.









Corporate Culture
Create and develop an understanding and appreciation of military culture within Cognizant


Leadership
Train leaders and managers on how to effectively interview, train and manage veterans 


Recruitment
Increase our veteran headcount through veteran-specific sourcing channels and methods


Onboarding
Assimilate veterans to Cognizant culture and ensure smooth integration into new role 


Career Growth/Support
Guide veterans on a career path within Cognizant and extend additional support to ensure retention 



Recognition
Through our efforts across CAMO to Cognizant's 5 strategic areas, our goal is to achieve veteran and military employee career success, enhancing our corporate brand and becoming known in veteran circles as a world class veteran career source.




                       
                      X




Each of our locations has a digital Wall of Honor displaying our highly valued Veterans of Cognizant.
Cognizant proudly partners with Donors Choose and provides funding to teachers of military children.
We are honored members of the 100,000 jobs mission coalition.






Cognizant has been named a 2015 Military Friendly Employer!






                       
