INNOVATION@COGNIZANT

Clients have a dual mandate:Run better for efficiencyRun different for growth
Cognizant is innovating new ways of doing business, experimenting with emerging technologies and business models. Our Innovation@Cognizant initiatives tackle the dual mandate and bring our clients the best technology and business expertise in today's digital world.LEARN MORE



Cognizant's investment in technologies like the SMAC stack bolster our business process expertise and contribute to our ability to define, build and evolve Code Halos for your business and your industry. 
Cognizant incubates the best intellectual property across our business units to bring you industry-focused solutions that keep challenging what's possible.
Our Global Innovation Ecosystem cultivates relationships between venture capital and private equity firms, academia, accelerators, startups, Cognizant and our clients. Together, we discover and enable new solutions that innovate business operations and customer service.



