About
Cognizant Technology Solutions Corp. is located at the address 1971 E 5th St in Tempe, Arizona 85281.  Cognizant Technology Solutions Corp. specializes in Desktop Publishing, Hiring & Recruiting, Security Audits.  Cognizant Technology Solutions Corp. has an annual sales volume of 2M – 4,999,999.  .For more information contact Brian  Rhynas, Owner or  go to www.cognizant.comCognizant Technology Solutions Corp. provides Systems Design, Database Design, Network Installation to it's customers.  For maps and directions to Cognizant Technology Solutions Corp. view the map to the right.  For reviews of Cognizant Technology Solutions Corp. see below.









